  Privacy Policy for Motiva                                                                                                                                                                                       
                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
  Last updated: April 28, 2026                                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
  Motiva ("the App") is a motivational quotes app. We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting it.                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
  Data Collection                                                                                                                                                                                                 
  - The App does not collect, store, or transmit any personal data to external servers.                                                                                                                           
  - Quotes you save and settings you configure are stored locally on your device using Apple's SwiftData framework.                                                                                               
  - If you submit feedback through the in-app form, your name, email (if provided), and message are sent to Formspree.io for delivery. We do not store this data beyond what Formspree retains. See Formspree's   
  privacy policy at https://formspree.io/legal/privacy-policy.                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
  Photos                                                                                                                                                                                                          
  - When you download wallpapers, images are saved to your device's Photos library in a "Motiva" album. The App does not access or read your existing photos.                                                     
                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
  Notifications                                                                                                                                                                                                   
  - If you enable notifications, they are scheduled locally on your device. No data is sent to any server.                                                                                                        
                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
  Analytics                                                                                                                                                                                                       
  - The App does not use any analytics, tracking, or advertising SDKs.                                                                                                                                            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
  Third-Party Services                                                                                                                                                                                            
  - Formspree.io (feedback form delivery only)                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
  Children's Privacy                                                                                                                                                                                              
  - The App does not knowingly collect data from children under 13.                                                                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
  Changes                                                                                                                                                                                                         
  - We may update this policy. Changes will be reflected in the "Last updated" date above.                                                                                                                        
                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
  Contact                                                                                                                                                                                                         
  - For questions about this policy, use the in-app feedback form.                                                                 
